name: Karakuri Cash Lodge
desc: Target 1 “Karakuri” monster you control and 1 Effect Monster your opponent controls; change the battle position of your targeted monster, and if you do, negate the effects of your opponent's targeted monster until the end of this turn. If you control a “Karakuri” monster: You can banish this card from the GY, then target 1 face-up monster; change its battle position. You can only activate 1 "Karakuri Cash Lodge" once per turn.
